https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/fL0psQFnroOkBpj3RLqkWJrnO2X.jpg In pre-revolution Cuba, Katey Miller is about to defy everyone's expectations. Instead of a parent-approved suitor, Katey is drawn to the sexy waiter, Javier, who spends his nights dancing in Havana's nightclubs. As she secretly learns to dance with Javier, she learns the meanings of love, sensuality and independence. Dirty Dancing: Havana Nights
